codex
The dump also shows the test cancels before the remote-agent path has necessarily observed the remote task ID. I’m changing the streaming request so parent cancellation cannot abort the remote stream before the first remote event is seen; once any remote task event is known, cancellation exits locally and the existing cleanup can cancel that remote task by ID.
